ChangeList.Description: Added the CRUD operations to the [corsConfiguration_v2](https://learn.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/corsConfiguration_v2?view=graph-rest-beta) resource. The resource represents the CORS settings for an on-premises wildcard application published through Microsoft Entra application proxy and accessed via HTTP.

Added the [ipApplicationSegment](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/ipApplicationSegment?view=graph-rest-beta) resource and its associated API operations.The resource represents the CORS settings for an on-premises nonweb application published through Microsoft Entra application proxy and accessed via HTTP.

Added the CRUD operations to the [webApplicationSegment](https://learn.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/webApplicationSegment?view=graph-rest-beta) resource. The resource represents the CORS settings for an on-premises wildcard application published through Microsoft Entra application proxy and accessed via HTTP.
Added the `isDnsResolutionEnabled` property to the [onPremisesPublishing](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/onPremisesPublishing?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
Added the `isAccessibleViaZTNAClient` property to the [onPremisesPublishing](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/onPremisesPublishing?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
Added the `useAlternateUrlForTranslationAndRedirect` property to the [onPremisesPublishing](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/onPremisesPublishing?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
Added the `isDefaultAccessEnabled` property to the [onPremisesPublishingProfile](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/onPremisesPublishingProfile?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
Added the `applicationSegments` relationship to the [onPremisesPublishingProfile](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/onPremisesPublishingProfile?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.

Added the [networkAccessRoot](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/networkaccess-networkAccessRoot?view=graph-rest-beta)  resource. This entity is the container for all APIs relating to the Global Secure Access service.

Added the [branchConnectivityConfiguration](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/networkaccess-branchConnectivityConfiguration?view=graph-rest-beta) resource and its associated method.
Added the **connectivityConfiguration** relationship to the [branchSite](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/networkaccess-branchSite?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
Added the `koreaSouth` member to the **region** enumeration.
Added the **zoneRedundancyPreSharedKey** property to the [tunnelConfiguration](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/networkaccess-tunnelConfiguration?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.

Deprecated the **branchSite** relationship on the [connectivity](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/networkaccess-connectivity?view=graph-rest-beta) resource. Use the **remoteNetworks** relationship instead
Added the **remoteNetworks** relationship to the [connectivity](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/networkaccess-connectivity?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.

Deprecated the [branchSite](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/networkaccess-branchsite?view=graph-rest-beta) resource and its associated methods, endpoints, and relationships. Use the [remoteNetwork](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/networkaccess-remoteNetwork?view=graph-rest-beta) resource and its associated methods, endpoints, and relationships instead.
Added the [remoteNetwork](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/networkaccess-remoteNetwork?view=graph-rest-beta) resource and its associated methods.

Added the [remoteNetworkConnectivityConfiguration](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/networkaccess-remoteNetworkConnectivityConfiguration?view=graph-rest-beta) resource and its associated methods.
Added the `italyNorth` member to the **region** enumeration.
Added the `franceSouth` member to the **region** enumeration.
Added the `israelCentral` member to the **region** enumeration.
Removed the **bandwidthCapacity** property from the [remoteNetwork](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/networkaccess-remoteNetwork?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
Removed the **connectivityState** property from the [remoteNetwork](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/networkaccess-remoteNetwork?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
Removed the **country** property from the [remoteNetwork](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/networkaccess-remoteNetwork?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
Added the **tls** relationship to the [networkAccessRoot](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/networkaccess-networkAccessRoot?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
Added the **tlsInspectionPolicies** relationship to the [networkAccessRoot](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/networkaccess-networkAccessRoot?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
Added the **threatIntelligencePolicies** relationship to the [networkAccessRoot](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/networkaccess-networkAccessRoot?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.

Removed the **enrichedAuditLogs** resource. Please note that we are modifying the way to consume Enriched Microsoft 365 logs [Learn more](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/entra/global-secure-access/how-to-view-enriched-logs)
Removed the **enrichedAuditLogs** relationship from the [settings](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/networkaccess-settings?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
